+= dst_step;^Jsrc_index += src_step;^J}^J}^J}^J}^J#endif^Jinline void Lab2BGR_f(const float * srcbuf, float * dstbuf,^J#ifdef SRGB^J__global const float * gammaTab,^J#endif^J__constant float * coeffs, coeffs[6], C7 = coeffs[7], C8 = coeffs[8];^Jfloat y, fy;^Jif (li <= lThresh)^J{^Jy = li / 903.3f;^Jfy = fma(7.787f, y, 16.0f / 116.0f);^J}^Jelse^J{^Jfy = (li + 16.0f) / 116.0f;^Jy = fy * fy * fy;^J}^Jfloat fxz[] = { ai / 500.0f + fy, fy - bi / 200.0f };^J#pragma unroll^Jfor (int j = 0; j < 2; j++)^Jif (fxz[j] <= fThresh)^Jfxz[j] = (fxz[j] - 16.0f / 116.0f) / 7.787f;^Jelse^Jfxz[j] = fxz[j]     \^Jbarrier(CLK_LOCAL_MEM_FENCE);^J#define noconvert^J#define DIG(a) a,^J__constant WT1 kernelData[] = { COEFF };^J__kernel void filter2D(__global const uchar * srcptr, int src_step, int srcOffsetX, int srcOffsetY, int srcEndX, int srcEndY,^J__global uchar * dstptr, int dst_step, int dst_offset, int rows, int cols, float delta)^J{^Jint local_id = get_local_id(0);^Jint x = local_id + (LOCAL_SIZE - (KERNEL_SIZE_X - 1)) * get_group_id(0) - ANCHOR_X;^Jint y = get_global_id(1);^JWT data[KERNEL_SIZE_Y];^J__local WT sumOfCols[LOCAL_SIZE];^J#ifdef BORDER_ISOLATED^Jint srcBeginX = srcOffsetX;^Jint srcBeginY = srcOffsetY;^J#else^Jint srcBeginX = 0;^Jint srcBeginY = 0;^J#endif^Jint srcX = srcOffsetX + x;^Jint srcY = srcOffsetY + y - ANCHOR_Y;^J__global dstT *dst = (__global dstT *)(dstptr + mad24(y, dst_step, mad24(x, DSTSIZE, dst_offset)));^J#ifdef BORDER_CONSTANT^Jif (srcX >= srcBeginX && srcX < srcEndX)^J{^Jfor (int sy = 0, sy_index = 0;   [ 55440]  #ifdef BORDER_REPLICATE^J#define ADDR_L(i, l_edge, r_edge)  ((i) <  (l_edge) ? (l_edge)   : (i))^J#define ADDR_R(i, r_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (r_edge) ? (r_edge)-1 : (addr))^J#define ADDR_H(i, t_edge, b_edge)  ((i) <  (t_edge) ? (t_edge)   :(i))^J#define ADDR_B(i, b_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (b_edge) ? (b_edge)-1 :(addr))^J#endif^J#ifdef BORDER_REFLECT^J#define ADDR_L(i, l_edge, r_edge)  ((i) <  (l_edge) ? -(i)-1               : (i))^J#define ADDR_R(i, r_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (r_edge) ? -(i)-1+((r_edge)<<1) : (addr))^J#define ADDR_H(i, t_edge, b_edge)  ((i) <  (t_edge) ? -(i)-1 : (i))^J#define ADDR_B(i, b_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (b_edge) ? -(i)-1+((b_edge)<<1) : (addr))^J#endif^J#ifdef BORDER_REFLECT_101^J#define ADDR_L(i, l_edge, r_edge)  ((i) <  (l_edge) ? -(i)                 : (i))^J#define ADDR_R(i, r_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (r_edge) ? -(i)-2+((r_edge)<<1) : (addr))^J#define ADDR_H(i, t_edge, b_edge)  ((i) <  (t_edge) ? -(i)                 : (i))^J#define ADDR_B(i, b_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (b_edge) ? -(i)-2+((b_edge)<<1) : (addr))^J#endif^J#ifdef BORDER_WRAP^J#define ADDR_L(i, l_edge, r_edge)  ((i) <  (l_edge) ? (i)+(r_edge) : (i))^J#define ADDR_R(i, r_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (r_edge) ? (i)-(r_edge) : (addr))^J#define ADDR_H(i, t_edge, b_edge)  ((i) <  (t_edge) ? (i)+(b_edge) : (i))^J#define ADDR_B(i, b_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (b_edge) ? (i)-(b_edge) : (addr))^J#endif^J#ifdef BORDER_ISOLATED^J#define ISOLATED_MIN(VAL) (VAL)^J#else^J#define ISOLATED_MIN(VAL) 0^J#endif^J#ifdef EXTRA_EXTRAPOLATION^J#ifdef BORDER_CONSTANT^J#elif defined BORDER_REPLICATE^J#define EXTRAPOLATE(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY) \^J{ \^Jx = max(min(x, maxX - 1), minX); \^Jy = max(min(y, maxY - 1), minY); \^J}^J#elif defined BORDER_WRAP^J#define EXTRAPOLATE(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY) \^J{ \^Jif (x < minX) \^Jx -= ((x - maxX + 1) / maxX) * maxX; \^Jif (x >= maxX) \^Jx %= maxX; \^Jif (y < minY) \^Jy -= ((y - maxY + 1) / maxY) * maxY; \^Jif (y >= maxY) \^Jy %= maxY; \^J}^J#elif defined(BORDER_REFLECT) || defined(BORDER_REFLECT_101)^J#define EXTRAPOLATE_(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY, delta) \^J{ \^Jif (maxX - minX == 1) \^Jx = minX; \^Jelse \^Jdo \^J{ \^Jif (x < minX) \^Jx = minX - (x - minX) - 1 + delta; \^Jelse \^Jx = maxX - 1 - (x - maxX) - delta; \^J} \^Jwhile (x >= maxX || x < minX); \^J\^Jif (maxY - minY == 1) \^Jy = minY; \^Jelse \^Jdo \^J{ \^Jif (y < minY) \^Jy = minY - (y - minY) - 1 + delta; \^Jelse \^Jy = maxY - 1 - (y - maxY) - delta; \^J} \^Jwhile (y >= maxY || y < minY); \^J}^J#ifdef BORDER_REFLECT^J#define EXTRAPOLATE(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY) EXTRAPOLATE_(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY, 0)^J#elif defined(BORDER_REFLECT_101) || defined(BORDER_REFLECT101)^J#define EXTRAPOLATE(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY) EXTRAPOLATE_(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY, 1)^J#endif^J#else^J#error No extrapolation method^J#endif^J#else^J#define EXTRAPOLATE(x, y, minX, minY, maxX, maxY) \^J{ \^Jint _row = y - ISOLATED_MIN(minY), _col = x - (l_edge)   : (i))^J#define ADDR_R(i, r_edge, addr)    ((i) >= (r_edge) ? unroll^Jfor (int i = 0; i < 16; i++)^Jsum = fma(v[i], tab1y[(i>>2)] * tab1x[(i&3)], sum);^Jstorepix(convertToT( sum ), dstptr + dst_index);^J#endif^J#else^J__constant float * coeffs_y = coeffs + (ay << 2), * coeffs_x = coeffs + (ax << 2);^Jint src_index0 = mad24(sy, src_step, mad24(sx, pixsize, src_offset)), src_index;^Jint dst_index = mad24(dy, dst_step, mad24(dx, pixsize, dst_offset));^JWT sum = (WT)(0), xsum;^J#pragma unroll^Jfor (int y = 0; y < 4; y++)^J{^Jsrc_index = mad24(y, src_step, src_index0);^Jif (sy + y >= 0 && sy + y < src_rows)^J{^Jxsum = (WT)(0);^Jif (sx >= 0 && sx + 4 < src_cols)^J{^J#if depth == 0 && cn == 1^Juchar4 value = vload4(0, srcptr + src_index);^Jxsum = dot(convert_float4(value), (float4)(coeffs_x[0], coeffs_x[1], coeffs_x[2], coeffs_x[3]));^J#else^J#pragma unroll^Jfor (int x = 0; x < 4; x++)^Jxsum = fma(convertToWT(loadpix(srcptr + mad24(x, pixsize, src_index))), coeffs_x[x], xsum);^J#endif^J}^Jelse^J{^J#pragma unroll^Jfor (int x = 0; x < 4; x++)^Jxsum = fma(sx + x >= 0 && sx + x < src_cols ?^JconvertToWT(loadpix(srcptr + mad24(x, pixsize, src_index))) : scalar, coeffs_x[x], xsum);^J}^Jsum = fma(xsum, coeffs_y[y], sum);^J}^Jelse^Jsum = fma(scalar,   [ 79c48]  #ifdef DOUBLE_SUPPORT^J#ifdef cl_amd_fp64^J#pragma OPENCL EXTENSION cl_amd_fp64:enable^J#elif defined (cl_khr_fp64)^J#pragma OPENCL EXTENSION cl_khr_fp64:enable^J#endif^J#define CT double^J#else^J#define CT float^J#endif^J#define INTER_BITS 5^J#define INTER_TAB_SIZE (1 << INTER_BITS)^J#define INTER_SCALE 1.f / INTER_TAB_SIZE^J#define AB_BITS max(10, (int)INTER_BITS)^J#define AB_SCALE (1 << AB_BITS)^J#define INTER_REMAP_COEF_BITS 15^J#define INTER_REMAP_COEF_SCALE (1 << INTER_REMAP_COEF_BITS)^J#define noconvert^J#ifndef ST^J#define ST T^J#endif^J#if cn != 3^J#define loadpix(addr)  *(__global const T*)(addr)^J#define storepix(val, addr)  *(__global T*)(addr) = val^J#define scalar scalar_^J#define pixsize (int)sizeof(T)^J#else^J#define loadpix(addr)  vload3(0, (__global const T1*)(addr))^J#define storepix(val, addr) vstore3(val, 0, (__global T1*)(addr))^J#ifdef INTER_NEAREST^J#define scalar (T)(scalar_.x, scalar_.y, scalar_.z)^J#else^J#define scalar (WT)(scalar_.x, scalar_.y, scalar_.z)^J#endif^J#define pixsize ((int)sizeof(T1)*3)^J#endif^J#ifdef INTER_NEAREST^J__kernel void warpPerspective(__global const uchar * srcptr, int src_step, int src_offset, int src_rows, int src_cols,^J__global uchar * dstptr, int dst_step, int dst_offset, int dst_rows, int dst_cols,^J__constant CT * M, ST scalar_)^J{^Jint dx = get_global_id(0);^Jint dy = get_global_id(1);^Jif (dx < dst_cols && dy < dst_rows)^J{^JCT X0 = M[0] * dx + M[1] * dy + M[2];^JCT Y0 = M[3] * dx + M[4] * dy + M[5];^JCT W = M[6] * dx + M[7] * dy + M[8];^JW = W != 0.0f ? 1.f / W : 0.0f;^Jshort sx = convert_short_sat_rte(X0*W);^Jshort sy = convert_short_sat_rte(Y0*W);^Jint dst_index = mad24(dy, dst_step, dx * pixsize + dst_offset);^Jif (sx >= 0 && sx < src_cols && sy >= 0 && sy < src_rows)^J{^Jint src_index = mad24(sy, src_step, sx * pixsize + src_offset);^Jstorepix(loadpix(srcptr + src_index), dstptr + dst_index);^J}^Jelse^Jstorepix(scalar, dstptr + dst_index);^J}^J}^J#elif defined INTER_LINEAR^J__kernel void warpPerspective(__global const uchar * srcptr, int src_step, int src_offset, int src_rows, int src_cols,^J__global uchar * dstptr, int dst_step, int dst_offset, int dst_rows, int dst_cols,^J__constant CT * M, ST scalar_)^J{^Jint dx = get_global_id(0);^Jint dy = get_global_id(1);^Jif (dx < dst_cols && dy < dst_rows)^J{^JCT X0 = M[0] * dx + M[1] * dy + M[2];^JCT Y0 = M[3] * dx + M[4] * dy + M[5];^JCT W = M[6] * dx + M[7] * dy + M[8];^JW = W != 0.0f ? INTER_TAB_SIZE / W : 0.0f;^Jint X = rint(X0 * W), Y = rint(Y0 * W);^Jshort sx = convert_short_sat(X >> INTER_BITS);^Jshort sy = convert_short_sat(Y >> INTER_BITS);^Jshort ay = (short)(Y & (INTER_TAB_SIZE - 1));^Jshort ax = (short)(X & (INTER_TAB_SIZE - 1));^JWT v0 = (sx >= 0 && sx < src_cols && sy >= 0 && sy < src_rows) ?^JconvertToWT(loadpix(srcptr + mad24(sy, src_step, src_offset + sx * pixsize))) : scalar;^JWT v1 = (sx+1 >= 0 && sx+1 < src_cols && sy >= 0 && sy < src_rows) ?^JconvertToWT(loadpix(srcptr + mad24(sy, src_step, src_offset + (sx+1) * pixsize))) : scalar;^JWT v2 = (sx >= 0 && sx < src_cols && sy+1 >= 0 && sy+1 < src_rows) ?^JconvertToWT(loadpix(srcptr + mad24(sy+1, src_step, src_offset + sx * pixsize))) : scalar;^JWT v3 = (sx+1 >= 0 && sx+1 < src_cols && sy+1 >= 0 && sy+1 < src_rows) ?^JconvertToWT(loadpix(srcptr + mad24(sy+1, src_step, src_offset + (sx+1) * pixsize))) : scalar;^Jfloat taby = 1.f/INTER_TAB_SIZE*ay;^Jfloat tabx = 1.f/INTER_TAB_SIZE*ax;^Jint dst_index = mad24(dy, dst_step, dst_offset + dx * pixsize);^J#if depth <= 4^Jint itab0 = convert_short_sat_rte( (1.0f-taby)*(1.0f-tabx) * INTER_REMAP_COEF_SCALE );^Jint itab1 = convert_short_sat_rte( (1.0f-taby)*tabx * INTER_REMAP_COEF_SCALE );^Jint itab2 = convert_short_sat_rte( taby*(1.0f-tabx) * INTER_REMAP_COEF_SCALE );^Jint itab3 = convert_short_sat_rte( taby*tabx * INTER_REMAP_COEF_SCALE );^JWT val = v0 * itab0 +  v1 * itab1 + v2 * itab2 + v3 * itab3;^Jstorepix(convertToT((val + (1 << (INTER_REMAP_COEF_BITS-1))) >> INTER_REMAP_COEF_BITS), dstptr + dst_index);^J#else^Jfloat tabx2 = 1.0f - 5.0f*A)*(x + 1.f) + 8.0f*A)*(x + 1.f) - 4.0f*A;^Jcoeffs[1] = ((A + 2.f)*x - (A + 3.f))*x*x + 1.f;^Jcoeffs[2] = ((A + 2.f)*(1.f - x) - (A + 3.f))*(1.f - x)*(1.f - x) + 1.f;^Jcoeffs[3] = 1.f - coeffs[0] - coeffs[1] - coeffs[2];^J}^J__kernel void warpPerspective(__global const uchar * srcptr, int src_step, int src_offset, int src_rows, int src_cols,^J__global uchar * dstptr, int dst_step, int dst_offset, int dst_rows, int dst_cols,^J__constant CT * M, ST scalar_)^J{^Jint dx = get_global_id(0);^Jint dy = get_global_id(1);^Jif (dx < dst_cols && dy < dst_rows)^J{^JCT X0 = M[0] * dx + M[1] * dy + M[2];^JCT Y0 = M[3] * dx + M[4] * dy + M[5];^JCT W = M[6] * dx + M[7] * dy + M[8];^JW = W != 0.0f ? u1NewVal) * (u1OldVal - u1NewVal);^Jfloat n2 = (u2OldVal - u2NewVal) * (u2OldVal - u2NewVal);^Jerror[y * I1wx_step + x] = n1 + n2;^J}^J}^J}^J

dv < dv1; ++dv, xmap_index += xmap_step,^Jymap_index += ymap_step)^J{^J__global float * xmap = (__global float *)(xmapptr + xmap_index);^J__global float * ymap = (__global float *)(ymapptr + ymap_index);^Jfloat v = tl_v + dv;^Jfloat y_ = fma(v, scale, -ct[1]);^Jfloat x = fma(ck_rinv[0], x_, fma(ck_rinv[1], y_, ck_rinv[2] * ct1));^Jfloat y = fma(ck_rinv[3], x_, fma(ck_rinv[4], y_, ck_rinv[5] * ct1));^Jfloat z = fma(ck_rinv[6], x_, fma(ck_rinv[7], y_, ck_rinv[8] * ct1));^Jif (z != 0)^Jx /= z, y /= z;^Jelse^Jx = y = -1;^Jxmap[0] = x;^Jymap[0] = y;^J}^J}^J}^J__kernel void buildWarpCylindricalMaps(__global uchar * xmapptr, int xmap_step, int xmap_offset,^J__global uchar * ymapptr, int ymap_step, int ymap_offset, int rows, int cols,^J__constant float * ck_rinv, int tl_u, int tl_v, float scale, int rowsPerWI)^J{^Jint du = get_global_id(0);^Jint dv0 = get_global_id(1) * rowsPerWI;^Jif (du < cols)^J{^Jint xmap_index = mad24(dv0, xmap_step, mad24(du, (int)sizeof(float), xmap_offset));^Jint ymap_index = mad24(dv0, ymap_step, mad24(du, (int)sizeof(float), ymap_offset));^Jfloat u = (tl_u + du) * scale;^Jfloat x_, z_;^Jx_ = sincos(u, &z_);^Jfor (int dv = dv0, dv1 = min(rows, dv0 + rowsPerWI); dv < dv1; ++dv, xmap_index += xmap_step,^Jymap_index += ymap_step)^J{^J__global float * xmap = (__global float *)(xmapptr + xmap_index);^J__global float * ymap = (__global float *)(ymapptr + ymap_index);^Jfloat y_ = (tl_v + dv) * scale;^Jfloat x, y, z;^Jx = fma(ck_rinv[0], x_, fma(ck_rinv[1], y_, ck_rinv[2] * z_));^Jy = fma(ck_rinv[3], x_, fma(ck_rinv[4], y_, ck_rinv[5] * z_));^Jz = fma(ck_rinv[6], x_, fma(ck_rinv[7], y_, ck_rinv[8] * z_));^Jif (z > 0)^Jx /= z, y /= z;^Jelse^Jx = y = -1;^Jxmap[0] = x;^Jymap[0] = y;^J}^J}^J}^J__kernel void buildWarpSphericalMaps(__global uchar * xmapptr, int xmap_step, int xmap_offset,^J__global uchar * ymapptr, int ymap_step, int ymap_offset, int rows, int cols,^J__constant float * ck_rinv, int tl_u, int tl_v, float scale, int rowsPerWI)^J{^Jint du = get_global_id(0);^Jint dv0 = get_global_id(1) * rowsPerWI;^Jif (du < cols)^J{^Jint xmap_index = mad24(dv0, xmap_step, mad24(du, (int)sizeof(float), xmap_offset));^Jint ymap_index = mad24(dv0, ymap_step, mad24(du, (int)sizeof(float), ymap_offset));^Jfloat u = (tl_u + du) * scale;^Jfloat cosu, sinu = sincos(u, &cosu);^Jfor (int dv = dv0, dv1 = min(rows, dv0 + rowsPerWI); dv < dv1; ++dv, xmap_index += xmap_step,^Jymap_index += ymap_step)^J{^J__global float * xmap = (__global float *)(xmapptr + xmap_index);^J__global float * ymap = (__global float *)(ymapptr + ymap_index);^Jfloat v = (tl_v + dv) * scale;^Jfloat cosv, sinv = sincos(v, &cosv);^Jfloat x_ = sinv * sinu;^Jfloat y_ = -cosv;^Jfloat z_ = sinv * cosu;^Jfloat x, y, z;^Jx = fma(ck_rinv[0], x_, fma(ck_rinv[1], y_, ck_rinv[2] * z_));^Jy = fma(ck_rinv[3], x_, fma(ck_rinv[4], y_, ck_rinv[5] * z_));^Jz = fma(ck_rinv[6], x_, fma(ck_rinv[7], y_, ck_rinv[8] * z_));^Jif (z > 0)^Jx /= z, y /= z;^Jelse^Jx = y = -1;^Jxmap[0] = x;^Jymap[0] = y;^J}^J}^J}^J
